dct_title_s: Palæstinæ in XII tribus divisæ plane nova et ad textum sacrum accommodatior descriptio
dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Bar scale on map given in "Mill. geograph".
Shows topography, drainage, boundaries of the territories of the twelve tribes of Israel, places of historical interest.
